   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Legal support for audit framework procurement</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Legal support for audit framework procurement</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">PLEASE REVIEW YOUR ANSWER AS THE QUESTION HAS BEEN CHANGED

UM i Kampala upphandlar ett lokalt ramavtal f&#xF6;r revisionstj&#xE4;nster som planerar att l&#xF6;pa fr&#xE5;n 2015-2017 med m&#xF6;jlighet till max 2 &#xE5;rs f&#xF6;rl&#xE4;ngning, se insatsnummer 51180080. Inom ramen f&#xF6;r denna upphandling beh&#xF6;ver UM st&#xF6;d f&#xF6;r att bed&#xF6;ma legala samt relaterade skall krav i utv&#xE4;rderingen, s&#xE4;rskilt d&#xE5; antal anbudsgivare vida &#xF6;versteg f&#xF6;rv&#xE4;ntan och d&#xE5; UM inte har tillr&#xE4;ckliga resurser f&#xF6;r att hantera alla anbuden s&#xE5; snabbt som &#xE4;r &#xF6;nskv&#xE4;rt.

D&#xE5; beloppet understiger direktupphandlingsgr&#xE4;nsen och d&#xE5; ambassaden har ett akut behov av assistans f&#xF6;r att hantera denna situation beslutas att direktupphandla en jurist som ambassaden har arbetat med tidigare vad g&#xE4;ller liknande uppdrag med tillfredsst&#xE4;llande resultat.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Embassy is in the process of procuring a framework agreement for audit services, see contribution 51180080 for description. In this process the Embassy needs support to evaluate the legal &quot;must have&quot; requirements, especially considering that the number of bids vastly exceeded expecations. The Embassy does not have the possibility to handle this situation as soon as is required for the process with  current resources. For this reason and since the amount is below the direct procurement level the Embassy decides to proceed with a direct procurement for legal services in regards to this procurement process.</narrative>
  </description>
